<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:41:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>2024年中国“两会”：GDP与美国差距拉大，“东风”会盛行吗？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3254126/chinas-two-sessions-2024-gdp-gap-us-widens-will-east-wind-prevail?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>许多人曾预测，到本世纪中叶，中国的国内生产总值将超过美国，但最近的趋势表明，这种互换可能还很遥远——即使它真的发生了。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 03:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3254126/chinas-two-sessions-2024-gdp-gap-us-widens-will-east-wind-prevail?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>2月份中国服务业活动增长势头减弱，但仍连续第14个月扩张</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3254171/chinas-services-activity-growth-momentum-softens-february-still-expands-14th-consecutive-month?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>周二公布的数据显示，中国财新/标普全球服务业采购经理人指数（PMI）从 1 月份的 52.7 微降至 52.5。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3254171/chinas-services-activity-growth-momentum-softens-february-still-expands-14th-consecutive-month?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国和朝鲜的“友谊年”对美国盟友来说不一定是坏消息</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3254043/china-and-north-koreas-friendship-year-need-not-be-bad-news-us-allies?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京和平壤建交75周年之际，正值首尔担心东京向朝鲜示好而受到冷落。鉴于北京放弃平壤或首尔没有意义，中国更有可能扮演调解人的角色。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3254043/china-and-north-koreas-friendship-year-need-not-be-bad-news-us-allies?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>事实如此：2024年中国“两会”——李强总理设定全年GDP增​​长5%左右的目标</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3254167/chinas-two-sessions-2024-premier-li-qiang-delivers-first-work-report?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在人们对经济状况日益担忧的情况下，总理在发表第一份工作报告时公布了今年的经济目标。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 00:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3254167/chinas-two-sessions-2024-premier-li-qiang-delivers-first-work-report?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国“新生产力”理念为经济转型带来新希望和新动力</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/policy/article/3254080/chinas-new-productive-forces-concept-offers-fresh-hope-and-impetus-economic-transformation?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>“新生产力”的概念表明，中国最高领导层已经意识到，依靠债务拉动投资拉动增长的传统模式已经达到了极限。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 23:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/policy/article/3254080/chinas-new-productive-forces-concept-offers-fresh-hope-and-impetus-economic-transformation?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国“两会”：最高立法机关誓言克服美国科技制裁</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3254142/chinas-two-sessions-2024-top-legislature-vows-overcome-us-tech-and-science-sanctions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>全国人大发言人表示，中国对美国遏制战略的反应不会是自我孤立，而是号召创新和自力更生，并补充说未来的立法将解决与人工智能和生物技术相关的安全和道德问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 22:00:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3254142/chinas-two-sessions-2024-top-legislature-vows-overcome-us-tech-and-science-sanctions?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>首尔表示，中国在科技进步方面超越韩国，输给对手是“不可接受且令人不安的”，这引发了反思</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3254127/china-surpasses-south-korea-tech-and-science-gains-seoul-says-unacceptable-and-upsetting-loss-rival?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>韩国的官方调查结果显示，北京近年来为提升中国科技实力所做的努力取得了巨大成效，这意味着首尔在追赶的过程中面临着艰巨的任务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3254127/china-surpasses-south-korea-tech-and-science-gains-seoul-says-unacceptable-and-upsetting-loss-rival?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>巴西最大的大豆城市寻求吸引中国对谷物压榨行业的投资</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/world/americas/article/3254160/brazils-top-soybean-city-seeks-lure-chinese-investments-grain-crushing-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>索里索市市长阿里·拉芬指出，虽然中方愿意接受其代表团的建议，但中粮集团倾向于在中国加工大豆</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:09:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/americas/article/3254160/brazils-top-soybean-city-seeks-lure-chinese-investments-grain-crushing-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国“两会”：代表称数字经济“盲目投资”可能有害</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3254125/chinas-two-sessions-2024-blind-investments-digital-economy-could-be-harmful-delegate-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国政府的一位经济顾问表示，地方政府在经济规划方面缺乏“意识”，并敦促地方政府在投资中国数字经济时利用现有的产业基础和当地资源。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3254125/chinas-two-sessions-2024-blind-investments-digital-economy-could-be-harmful-delegate-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国“两会”：代表称免税额翻倍将“敢于消费”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3254117/chinas-two-sessions-2024-doubling-tax-free-allowance-will-dare-people-spend-delegate-say?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>全国人民代表大会代表张学武表示，他将提出一项建议，将中国的免税津贴增加一倍，达到每月 10,000 元人民币（1,389 美元），以促进消费。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3254117/chinas-two-sessions-2024-doubling-tax-free-allowance-will-dare-people-spend-delegate-say?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>北京负责香港事务的最高领导人要求香港在“23条”立法过程中防范可能的破坏</title><link>https://www.scmp.com